<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <!-- PRIMARY META -->
    <title>WAJAR.AI — Belajar apa aja, cukup WA aja</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Chat AI via WhatsApp. Gratis 8.000 kata pertama. Belajar coding, masak, ngaji, matematika & ide usaha cuma lewat WA. Rp1.000/jam. Dari Pondok Informatika Makassar.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="WAJAR.AI, asisten AI WhatsApp, belajar via WA, guru AI Indonesia, Pondok Informatika, AI Makassar, chatbot Indonesia">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="author" content="Pondok Informatika Makassar">

    <!-- OPEN GRAPH -->
    <meta property="og:title" content="WAJAR.AI — Belajar apa aja, cukup WA aja">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Gratis 8.000 kata pertama. Belajar apa aja lewat WhatsApp.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://wajar.pondokinformatika.id/hero-poster.png">
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1080">
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="1350">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://wajar.pondokinformatika.id">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="WAJAR.AI">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="id_ID">

    <!-- TWITTER CARD -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="WAJAR.AI — Belajar apa aja, cukup WA aja">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Guru AI di WhatsApp. Gratis 8.000 kata pertama. Rp1.000/jam.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://wajar.pondokinformatika.id/hero-poster.png">

    <!-- FONTS -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* ===== RESET & VARIABLES ===== */
        :root {
            --cream: #fdf8f0;
            --cream-dark: #f5ede0;
            --navy: #0a1628;
            --navy-light: #162d50;
            --accent: #d4822e;
            --accent-light: #f0b86e;
            --accent-glow: rgba(212,130,46,0.15);
            --green: #2ecc71;
            --text: #1a1a2e;
            --text-muted: #7a7a8a;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --card-border: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            --shadow-lg: 0 8px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            --radius: 16px;
            --radius-sm: 10px;
            --radius-lg: 24px;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(10,22,40,0.92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            padding: 12px 0;
        }
        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .nav-brand {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .nav-brand span { color: var(--accent); }
        .nav-cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-cta:hover {
            background: #c07528;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* ===== HERO — PURE MOBILE LAYOUT ===== */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero .poster-wrap {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .hero .poster-img {
            width: 280px;
            max-width: 85%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            display: block;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .hero .poster-img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
        .hero .tagline {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }
        .hero .cta-wrap {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .hero .cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 280px;
            transition: all 0.25s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px var(--accent-glow);
        }
        .hero .cta:hover {
            background: #c07528;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 24px var(--accent-glow);
        }
        .hero .cta-sub {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* ===== SECTIONS ===== */
        section { padding: 48px 0; }
        section:nth-child(even) { background: var(--cream); }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .section-heading {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .section-sub {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* ===== HERO PROMO BANNER ===== */
        .hero-promo {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow), rgba(46,204,113,0.08));
            border: 1px solid rgba(212,130,46,0.15);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 14px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--navy);
        }
        .hero-promo strong { color: var(--accent); }

        /* ===== STEPS ===== */
        .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 16px 18px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .step:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .step-num {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: white;
        }
        .step-body { flex: 1; }
        .step-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
        .step-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 2px; }

        /* ===== GRID FITUR ===== */
        .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
        .feat {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .feat:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .feat-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .feat-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
        .feat-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 2px; }

        /* ===== PRICING ===== */
        .price-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .price-row:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .price-row.highlight {
            border: 2px solid var(--accent);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef9f0, #fff6e5);
            position: relative;
        }
        .price-row.highlight::before {
            content: '⭐ TERLARIS';
            position: absolute;
            top: -9px; right: 14px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .price-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
        .price-label small {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 1px;
        }
        .price-amount { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); white-space: nowrap; }
        .price-row.highlight .price-amount { font-size: 22px; }

        /* ===== QRIS ===== */
        .qris-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .qris-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .qris-desc {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .qris-img {
            width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .qris-note {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .qris-note strong { color: var(--text); }

        /* ===== TESTIMONIALS ===== */
        .testi {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .testi:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .testi p { font-style: italic; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .testi-author {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .testi-author small {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 1px;
        }
        .testi + .testi { margin-top: 10px; }

        /* ===== FAQ ===== */
        .faq-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding: 14px 0;
        }
        .faq-q {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text);
            cursor: default;
        }
        .faq-a {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* ===== CTA SECTION ===== */
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 56px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .cta-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin: 10px 0 24px;
            max-width: 320px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .cta-section .cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--accent-glow);
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }
        .cta-section .cta:hover {
            background: #c07528;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 28px var(--accent-glow);
        }
        .cta-footer-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            background: var(--navy);
            border-top: none;
        }
        footer p { margin-top: 4px; }
        footer strong { color: white; font-size: 15px; }
        footer span.accent { color: var(--accent); }
        footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        footer .footer-tagline {
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        footer .footer-attr {
            font-size: 11px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        footer .footer-copy {
            font-size: 10px;
            opacity: 0.4;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* ===== RESPONSIVE (untuk layar > 480px tetap mobile) ===== */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 420px;
            }
            .hero .poster-img {
                width: 260px;
            }
            .grid-2 {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero .poster-img { width: 250px; }
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
            .grid-2 .feat { padding: 14px; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 360px) {
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero .poster-img { width: 220px; }
        }
    </style>

    <!-- STRUCTURED DATA -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "WebSite",
        "name": "WAJAR.AI",
        "url": "https://wajar.pondokinformatika.id/",
        "description": "Asisten belajar AI lewat WhatsApp. Gratis cobain dulu.",
        "provider": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Pondok Informatika",
            "url": "https://pondokinformatika.id"
        },
        "inLanguage": "id-ID"
    }
    </script>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="nav-brand">WAJAR.<span>AI</span></div>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="https://wa.me/6282189456728?text=Halo+Aiman%2C+gratis+dong" target="_blank">💬 Coba Gratis</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO → Mobile-first: gambar tengah, teks bawah -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="poster-wrap">
            <img src="hero-poster.png" alt="WAJAR.AI — Guru Ngopi Sejati" class="poster-img" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <p class="tagline">Belajar apa aja, cukup WA aja</p>
        <div class="cta-wrap">
            <a class="cta" href="https://wa.me/6282189456728?text=Halo+Aiman%2C+gratis+dong" target="_blank">💬 Chat Aiman Gratis</a>
            <span class="cta-sub">🎁 8.000 kata pertama gratis</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CARA KERJA -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-promo">🎁 <strong>8.000 kata gratis</strong> — cobain dulu, kalau suka baru bayar</div>
        <div class="section-title">Cara Kerja</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Gampang banget</h2>
        <div class="section-sub">Cukup WhatsApp yang udah ada.</div>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <div class="step-body">
                    <div class="step-title">Chat nomor WAJAR.AI</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">Buka WhatsApp, chat nomor WAJAR.AI, tanya apa aja.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <div class="step-body">
                    <div class="step-title">Tanya apa pun</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">Resep masak, PR anak, draft surat, curhat, ide bisnis — semua dijawab.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <div class="step-body">
                    <div class="step-title">Kalau suka, bayar</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">8.000 kata gratis dulu. Kalau feels right, pilih paket langganan.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- LAYANAN -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">Layanan</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Bisa buat apa aja?</h2>
        <div class="section-sub">Beneran apa aja. Coba aja chat.</div>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">📚</div><div class="feat-title">Belajar & PR</div><div class="feat-desc">Matematika, bahasa, coding — sampe UAS juga dibantu.</div></div>
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">🍳</div><div class="feat-title">Resep & Harian</div><div class="feat-desc">Resep masak, jadwal, draft surat, ide konten.</div></div>
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">💡</div><div class="feat-title">Ide & Bisnis</div><div class="feat-desc">Brainstorming, proposal, strategi marketing.</div></div>
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">🤲</div><div class="feat-title">Curhat & Spiritual</div><div class="feat-desc">Buat yang butuh temen ngobrol atau tanya-tanya agama.</div></div>
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">💻</div><div class="feat-title">Coding & IT</div><div class="feat-desc">HTML, Python, database, project IT — tanya aja.</div></div>
            <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">🎯</div><div class="feat-title">Lainnya</div><div class="feat-desc">Pokoknya apa aja. Chat aja, kalau gak bisa ya bilang.</div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- HARGA -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">Harga</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Murah banget</h2>
        <div class="section-sub">Semurah ngopi. Gratis cobain dulu.</div>
        <div class="price-row highlight">
            <div class="price-label">🎁 Starter Gratis<small>8.000 kata pertama — cobain dulu</small></div>
            <div class="price-amount">Rp0</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price-label">☕ Per Jam<small>Pas butuh dadakan</small></div>
            <div class="price-amount">Rp1.000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price-label">📅 Per Hari<small>Seharian penuh tanya-tanya</small></div>
            <div class="price-amount">Rp10.000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price-label">📆 Per Minggu<small>Pas ada project atau ujian</small></div>
            <div class="price-amount">Rp50.000</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-row">
            <div class="price-label">🌙 Per Bulan<small>Paling hemat — kurang dari segelas kopi/hari</small></div>
            <div class="price-amount">Rp150.000</div>
        </div>

        <!-- QRIS -->
        <div class="qris-section">
            <div class="qris-label">💳 Bayar via QRIS</div>
            <p class="qris-desc">Transfer sesuai nominal di atas. Kirim bukti ke Aiman via WA untuk aktivasi.</p>
            <img src="qris.png" alt="QRIS WAJAR.AI" class="qris-img" loading="lazy" />
            <p class="qris-note">Setelah transfer, chat Aiman: <strong>"Udah transfer [nominal]"</strong> ✅</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONI -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">Testimoni</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Kata mereka</h2>
        <div class="section-sub">Yang udah coba, pada bilang...</div>
        <div class="testi">
            <p>"Bu guru kalau lagi sibuk, tinggal chat WAJAR.AI. Santai."</p>
            <div class="testi-author">— Ustadz Hasan <small>Guru Ngaji, Makassar</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="testi">
            <p>"Pake buat bikin konten medsos masjid. Cepet banget."</p>
            <div class="testi-author">— Kak Rina <small>Admin Medsos Masjid</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="testi">
            <p>"Ngajarin anak PR matematika. Dulu stress, sekarang tinggal foto soal kirim ke WA."</p>
            <div class="testi-author">— Ibu Dewi <small>Orang Tua Santri</small></div>
        </div>
